    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>10pm, September 4th, 1997.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The reclusive Detective Lambda is contacted by the F.B.I. to consult on a deadly case of arson. Can Lambda bring down the charismatic cult leader at the center of the mystery? It's time for the ultimate battle of wits! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daemon Masquerade is a supernatural detective game inspired by anime like Death Note and Fate/stay night, and games such as the Ace Attorney series.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Organize the Evidence</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/e78c36e0edebab9caeb03e2af6d98a9e.poster.avif?t=1730340876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/e78c36e0edebab9caeb03e2af6d98a9e.webm?t=1730340876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/e78c36e0edebab9caeb03e2af6d98a9e.mp4?t=1730340876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meticulously sort the clues on your pinboard however you see fit. Do you prefer the neat orderly rows of a professional detective, or the scattered piles of a conspiracy theorist? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Annotate your Thoughts</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/0b157a3f1425dc9a7ef3850928c140d3.poster.avif?t=1730340876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/0b157a3f1425dc9a7ef3850928c140d3.webm?t=1730340876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/0b157a3f1425dc9a7ef3850928c140d3.mp4?t=1730340876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's no need to fetch a pen and paper, scribble your notes directly onto the evidence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deduce the Truth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/fd5241384761f9203b47d7f190a521fb.poster.avif?t=1730340876\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/fd5241384761f9203b47d7f190a521fb.webm?t=1730340876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/fd5241384761f9203b47d7f190a521fb.mp4?t=1730340876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Thread of Logic deduction system allows you to solve cases in multiple ways, just as long as you've got the facts to back up your theories.</p>",
